Package: libfdk0
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends},
 libfreetype6,
 libwayland-client0,
 libx11-6,
 libxcursor1
Description: Faded Dream Kit — lightweight GUI toolkit (shared library)
 FDK is a from-scratch GUI toolkit for Linux with Wayland and X11 backends,
 software and OpenGL rendering, and a built-in theming system. No D-Bus,
 no GTK, no systemd dependencies.

Package: libfdk-dev
Architecture: any
Depends: libfdk0 (= ${binary:Version}), ${misc:Depends}
Description: Faded Dream Kit — development files
 Headers, static library, pkg-config file, and CMake config for building
 applications with FDK.

Package: fdk-theme
Architecture: any
Depends: libfdk0 (= ${binary:Version}), ${misc:Depends}
Description: Faded Dream Kit — theme management CLI
 Command-line tool for setting, listing, and inspecting FDK themes.
 Manages ~/.FDKthemes/ and ~/.config/FDK/fdk.conf.
